These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, filmmaking, reading, collecting
There 4 different types of food: orange, cucumber, grapefruit, eggplant
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, lily, azalea
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, chess, go
 1. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsazalea is the person eating cucumber##1
 5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 6. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
10. the person who growsazalea is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
11. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growslily##1
12. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
13. the person playing go is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting    | filmmaking | reading    | skydiving   |
| Food   | orange | grapefruit | cucumber | eggplant |
| Flower           | aconite       | lily   | azalea  | amaryllis     |
| Game     | bridge      | chess   | go    | billiard    |

