The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, card-games, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
 3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person traveling to liverpool##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
10. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
11. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
