 1. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who likes white##7
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
 6. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is not the person who likes coral##6
 8. the person who likes white is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
10. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
