 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person playing bridge is not the person driving the ship##6
 6. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the japanese##1
 8. the indian is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing bridge##7
 9. the indian is the person driving the ship##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
11. the spanish is not the person driving the ship##6

.:: Answer ::.
