 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the mechanic##1
 3. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the project-manager##1
 5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 7. the mechanic is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
 8. the social-worker is not the prince-smoker##6
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
12. the mechanic is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job         | freelancer      | mechanic   | social-worker   | project-manager       |
| City   | rome | hannover    | paris | colone       |
| Birthday   | january  | february | may   | july     |
| Cigar         | prince   | dannemann    | bolivar   | siglo |

