.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, bike, skateboard
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, bridge, mah-jongg
House: cottage, ranch-style, modern, futuristic
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, lawyer, social-worker, dressmaker
 1. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
 3. the futuristic house is between the dressmaker and the social-worker##2
 4. the cottage house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing billiard is not the lawyer##6
 6. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person playing mah-jongg##7
 8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
 9. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the futuristic house##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person playing bridge is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | motorbike   | skateboard     | bike   | subway |
| Game       | mah-jongg   | scrabble | billiard | bridge    |
| House      | modern | futuristic | cottage   | ranch-style  |
| Job        | dressmaker | videographer     | social-worker   | lawyer |

