.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, march, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, cycling, golf
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, spy, sports, documentary
House: art-deco, cottage, modern, palace
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 2. the art-deco house is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person watching romance movies##2
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the cottage house is not the person watching sports movies##6
 7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
 8. the art-deco house is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the person watching documentary movies is not the person who's sport is golf##6
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
11. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the palace house##1
12. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
13. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
14. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
15. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday      | april      | november        | may          | march    |
| Sport         | golf | basketball    | cycling          | volleyball |
| Movie-Genre           | romance  | spy   | sports | documentary      |
| House   | palace       | art-deco | modern          | cottage        |

