.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, aconite, daffodil
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, white, ebony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, electronic, indie, rock
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, poker, canasta
 1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 2. the person who likes white is the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person playing snooker is the fan rock##1
 4. the fan indie is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsdahlia##2
 5. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
 6. the fan metal is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who growsazalea##7
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
 8. the fan metal is the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
10. the fan electronic is on the far right##1
11. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower   | daffodil      | aconite     | dahlia   | azalea    |
| Color     | ebony | white   | orange | black |
| Music-Genre     | rock        | indie     | metal  | electronic      |
| Game   | snooker       | canasta | monopoly   | poker    |

 